parameters: Chairman: "For some reason, my hypnosis didn't work on Miss Karen..."

Tsukeshiba: "Are you suggesting that the device I developed was
defective?"
Chairman: "No, that's not what I mean..."

Tsukeshiba: "If you're useless... then there's no need for you
anymore."

Tsukeshiba: "Katsuhiro, take care of it. I have no need for failures
among my subordinates..."
Katsuhiro: "Well, well... if it isn't Miss Karen."

Katsuhiro: "What are you doing in a place like this? Eavesdropping
isn't very nice."
Karen: "Katsuhiro, if you come any closer, I'll kill you!"
Karen: "What do you intend to do with me..."
Katsuhiro: "President Tsukeshiba, what should we do?"
Tsukeshiba: "So you've been discovered. Can't be helped."
Tsukeshiba: "Karen-san, come into the room. I'll tell you everything."

Karen: "Katsuhiro, move! Don't get in my line of sight anymore. You're
disgusting!"
